{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WQoEsCGR14GF739u8t2H1h","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are the complete findings for the Round 2 best StepML regime ensemble artifact JSON files.\n\n---\n\n## Location: h3-secondary-method-calibration/output/calibrated_artifacts/\n\nAll 5 files reside at:\n```\n/Users/dipanwitaguhathakurta/Downloads/inference-sim-package/BLIS-research/hypotheses/h-stepml/round2/idea-2-regime-ensemble/h3-secondary-method-calibration/output/calibrated_artifacts/\n```\n\nThese are the \"best\" (calibrated) versions of the regime ensemble artifacts -- they went through secondary method calibration (h3) which refined overhead constants on top of the h1 base regime models.\n\n---\n\n### 1. `/Users/dipanwitaguhathakurta/Downloads/inference-sim-package/BLIS-research/hypotheses/h-stepml/round2/idea-2-regime-ensemble/h3-secondary-method-calibration/output/calibrated_artifacts/llama-2-7b_tp1_regime.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"version\": 2,\n  \"step_time_regimes\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"decode_only\",\n      \"condition\": { \"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\", \"op\": \"==\", \"value\": 0 },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -37.37132221350058,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"decode_tokens\": 7.951495295146752,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 7.951495295147041\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"mixed_light\",\n      \"condition\": { \"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\", \"op\": \"<\", \"value\": 256 },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -77.97943712885353,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"prefill_tokens\": 28.707846070521985,\n          \"decode_tokens\": 8.238725686646465,\n          \"num_prefill_reqs\": 48.63455190521838,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 8.238725687421233,\n          \"prefill_x_decode\": -0.15969273704853537,\n          \"prefill_sq\": -0.8113619055257316\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"step_overhead_us\": 3896.7631749593834,\n  \"output_token_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"scheduling_processing_time_us\": 202.036,\n  \"preemption_processing_time_us\": 0,\n  \"queueing_time\": {\n    \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n    \"intercept\": 202.036,\n    \"feature_coefficients\": {}\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Key characteristics:** Smallest model (7B, TP1). Lowest step overhead (3897 us). No KV features in either regime (small model does not exhibit KV-dependent step time). decode_only intercept is near zero (-37). Scheduling time 202 us.\n\n---\n\n### 2. `/Users/dipanwitaguhathakurta/Downloads/inference-sim-package/BLIS-research/hypotheses/h-stepml/round2/idea-2-regime-ensemble/h3-secondary-method-calibration/output/calibrated_artifacts/codellama-34b_tp2_regime.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"version\": 2,\n  \"step_time_regimes\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"decode_only\",\n      \"condition\": { \"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\", \"op\": \"==\", \"value\": 0 },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": 35.853323858800906,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"decode_tokens\": 3.5925069858883565,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 3.5925069858920695,\n          \"kv_sum\": 0.020150605312553797,\n          \"kv_max\": -1.757923914365141,\n          \"kv_mean\": -1.7397273613209323,\n          \"kv_std\": 5.006425637573251,\n          \"decode_x_kv_mean\": 0.0879261265445312\n        }\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"name\": \"mixed_light\",\n      \"condition\": { \"feature\": \"prefill_tokens\", \"op\": \"<\", \"value\": 256 },\n      \"model\": {\n        \"model_type\": \"linear\",\n        \"intercept\": -1367.6689004644509,\n        \"feature_coefficients\": {\n          \"prefill_tokens\": 31.42096377076365,\n          \"decode_tokens\": 33.79272044308543,\n          \"num_prefill_reqs\": -36.358679515809705,\n          \"num_decode_reqs\": 33.792720213932