{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_bdrk_01XQ7VBdV5p7VKPjYRAj1w3p","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"claude-opus-4-6","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_014d1AQ46dBRXeCRMzDmQbAf","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"# First, test manually with a lifecycle→trace CSV conversion and stepml artifact\npython3 -c \"\nimport json, random, sys, os\nGT = '/Users/dipanwitaguhathakurta/Downloads/inference-sim-package/BLIS-research/eval/ground_truth/20260217-162547-llama-2-7b-tp1-roleplay'\nlc_path = os.path.join(GT, 'results', 'per_request_lifecycle_metrics.json')\nwith open(lc_path) as f:\n    data = json.load(f)\nprint(f'Loaded {len(data)} requests')\nbase_time = min(e['start_time'] for e in data)\nduration = max(e['start_time'] for e in data) - base_time\nprint(f'Duration: {duration:.1f}s')\n\n# Create a minimal CSV trace\nrng = random.Random(42)\ncsv_path = '/tmp/test_trace.csv'\nwith open(csv_path, 'w') as f:\n    f.write('arrival_time,request_id,model,prefill_tokens,decode_tokens\\n')\n    for i, entry in enumerate(data[:5]):\n        info = entry.get('info', {})\n        input_count = info.get('input_tokens', 10)\n        output_count = info.get('output_tokens', 10)\n        arrival = entry['start_time'] - base_time\n        inp = [rng.randint(0,31999) for _ in range(input_count)]\n        out = [rng.randint(0,31999) for _ in range(output_count)]\n        f.write(f'{arrival:.6f},request_{i},meta-llama/Llama-2-7b-hf,\\\"{json.dumps(inp)}\\\",\\\"{json.dumps(out)}\\\"\\n')\nprint('Wrote test trace CSV with 5 requests')\n\" 2>&1","description":"Test trace CSV creation"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"output_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5cda49b4-0eac-4d7d-a6da-e3880a46a823","uuid":"492a6310-e97c-4a5d-a2c8-a688e80d44f3"}
